<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/abena-oppong-asare> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Abena Oppong-Asare was Parliamentary Secretary at the Cabinet Office between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Erith and Thamesmead in December 2019."@en .
